          "description": "The people at the facility who care for you are lovely and kind to deal with, the surgery went well.\n\nHowever, the facility called me and asked me to move my surgery from a day that was considered in-network to the following day which was considered out-of-network. I was told they had checked and I would be charged a specified amount and not to worry. Well 8 months later they got around to sending me a statement that was approximately 25% higher than originally being told. Don't they deal with insurance everyday? But sure tell someone one amount and wait months and charge them 25% more than you told them. Poorly done.",
