          "description": "I would just like to say thank you to the staff at Midtown Surgery Center.  Tim the anesthesiologist was super nice, he reassured me that I would be fine because I was super nervous. Cory my nurse was sweet as pie she took good care of me, And Rai was also very kind, he gave me some words of encouragement and he helped calm my nerves. I truly appreciate you all.",
